# NVC native Bazel build configuration.
#
# The build is intentionally plain: bzlmod is the default in Bazel 9, the nvc
# executable links dynamically (required so the JIT's foreign-function
# interface can resolve the runtime support symbols exported with -rdynamic),
# and no special toolchain flags are needed.

# Keep test output readable when/if tests are added.
test --test_output=errors
